OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of Britons would
OL,4,Cback smoke-free pub gardens ` poll
OL,6,FAlmost two thirds of people in Britain
OL,7,Fwould back a ban on smoking in pub
OL,8,Fgardens, according to a new survey.
OL,10,FThe move would be one of a handful of
OL,11,F"common sense" next steps to "support
OL,12,Fa smoke-free generation", according to
OL,13,Fthe charity Action on Smoking and
OL,14,FHealth (Ash).
OL,16,FThe majority of people also backed a
OL,17,Fban on smoking in areas such as
OL,18,Funiversity campuses and bus stops,
OL,19,Fwhile more than nine in 10 said smoke-
OL,20,Ffree laws should be extended to
OL,21,Fchildren's play areas.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@NO]sD@^OUtD@XO]
