OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778652345
OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of Britons would
OL,4,Cback smoke-free pub gardens ` poll
OL,6,FLast month, the UK became the first
OL,7,Fcountry in Europe to bring in laws to
OL,8,Fprevent children aged 17 or younger
OL,9,Ffrom ever legally buying cigarettes as
OL,10,Fthe Tobacco and Vapes Bill was given
OL,11,Froyal assent.
OL,13,FA Government consultation seeking
OL,14,Fviews on extending smoke-free laws to
OL,15,Fcertain outdoor spaces such as
OL,16,Fplaygrounds or outside hospitals, as
OL,17,Fwell as creating vape-free spaces,
OL,18,Falso closed on May 8.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
