CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778652345
OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of Britons would
OL,4,Cback smoke-free pub gardens ` poll
OL,6,FThe new YouGov poll of 13,259 people,
OL,7,Fconducted for Ash, found 93% of adults
OL,8,Fsupported smoke-free playgrounds,
OL,9,Falong with 78% who backed smoke-free
OL,10,Fbus stops.
OL,12,FSome 62% said they would support smoke-
OL,13,Ffree laws being extended to outdoor
OL,14,Fhospitality areas, such as pub
OL,15,Fgardens, while 68% supported smoke-
OL,16,Ffree university and college campuses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
