FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778652345
OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of Britons would
OL,4,Cback smoke-free pub gardens ` poll
OL,6,FAsh is also calling on the Government
OL,7,Fto develop a plan to reduce smoking in
OL,8,Fthe home, particularly around children.
OL,10,FIt also said there should be a vape-
OL,11,Ffree exemption applied in smoking
OL,12,Fcessation services to ensure smokers
OL,13,Fare still encouraged to switch to e-
OL,14,Fcigarettes to quit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
