PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778652345
OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of Britons would
OL,4,Cback smoke-free pub gardens ` poll
OL,6,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "The Tobacco and
OL,8,FVapes Act is a historic step towards
OL,9,FBritain's first smoke-free generation,
OL,10,Fprotecting them from the harms of
OL,11,Fsmoking and delivering on our ambition
OL,12,Ffor a smoke-free UK.
OL,14,F"Our consultation on free-from places
OL,15,Fclosed on Friday and we are carefully
OL,16,Fconsidering responses.
OL,26,@oD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
