FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778652345
OL,3,CAlmost two thirds of Britons would
OL,4,Cback smoke-free pub gardens ` poll
OL,6,F"As part of the consultation, we set
OL,7,Fout our proposals to make a number of
OL,8,Fsettings smoke, vape and heated
OL,9,Ftobacco-free ` including kids
OL,10,Fplaygrounds and outside schools. We
OL,11,Falso proposed making indoor spaces
OL,12,Fwhere smoking is already banned vape-
OL,13,Ffree and heated tobacco-free.
OL,15,F"This strikes the right balance right
OL,16,Fbetween protecting the most vulnerable
OL,17,Fand limiting any potential negative
OL,18,Fimpacts on businesses."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@WO]
